arStrings.szText: I got day-old bread and these fun rocks I found. The bread's not so bad if you toast it.
Friendly. Naive. Happy someone is talking to him, since most ignore him.
My best sellers were my carved charger tusks. If you carve the right pattern, they're good luck! That's what Da told me.
I'm all out of tusks, though. And money...oh, but if you bring me some tusks, I'll cut you in on the profits!
